article_title: Lawmakers want MinnesotaCare publicly sold to help address insurance costs
article_text:
Mankato, MN (56001)

Today

Thunderstorms likely this morning. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms this afternoon. High 76F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Cloudy skies this evening followed by thunderstorms late. A few storms may be severe. Low 61F. Winds ENE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author:
Trey Mewes
tmewes@mankatofreepress.com

og.description: Increasing insurance costs have prompted area legislators to propose adding MinnesotaCare to the MNsure health exchange system.
